Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不久之后天神即将降临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.31,0:00:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,人类这一种族或许要面临极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有成为御姿的勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,假若能按计划完成神婚仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,从神树大人那获得新的力量的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,又得强迫她们经历残酷的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是无力的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,仅能侧耳倾听与诚心祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所谓勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是被选中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,此乃至高的荣誉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没有其他的办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为了保护神性低下的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最后的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,大家化身一体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将得到拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那种形态 究竟能被称作是活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你的话有点太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,此后的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不是仅为人类的我们能改变得了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,交托给勇者大人和神树大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,关于勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她们是否会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妨碍仪式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果变成那样 再加上天神的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,事态怕是会一发不可收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,倘若如此 我们就接受现实吧\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.41,0:01:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这便是我们的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,纵使人世终结
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人的灵魂亦将与地神同在 永存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,与神树大人同在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,与神树大人同在
Comment: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:57.18,Title,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k20}我{\k20}的{\k20}心{\k20}在{\k20}燃{\k20}烧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:03:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,知晓人类的力量了吗 天神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这样 小鹫她们就能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,树 现在的我只会拖后腿 放我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么 夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我决不允许这种事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去和姐姐她们汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,夺回友奈 带上所有人一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡 能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,道路就由我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,开辟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡 拜托了 你一定要抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,再这样失去任何一个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我都无法原谅自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我变成怎样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以求求你 求你了 神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,树…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她没事吧 一定要活着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要带走友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不干坏事就无法存在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不承认是神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们牺牲了太多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,为国牺牲也是无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信那是高尚且正确的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我深爱着这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,凭借精灵的力量能回得去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧 友奈 我来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不惜这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,也不愿意将她交给我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 我现在就来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 是我 必须是由我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不然世界就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想要失去友奈你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你不明白我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,必须由我来做 这只有我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事不做也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真不像东乡的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是最为国家着想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是必须有人来做 别无选择的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什么别无选择 那种东西怎样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再被夺走重要的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么又在说冠冕堂皇的的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要一直忍耐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因为只需要我一个人忍耐下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,说出你的真心话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果害怕就讲出来 告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说你不想做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们是朋友的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就说救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我好怕 但是我不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想和大家分别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:09:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们明明已经这么拼命了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是使命所以无可奈何什么的都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,永远 永远
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,想和大家永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 把手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会 居然做到这种程度也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会 居然做到这种程度也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,救…救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,东…乡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事情 我们并没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很感激 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,舍弃人类的身份 舍弃朋友才能获得的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,世上有各种各样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,即使如此 如果您真的想拯救人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,能否
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,相信人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:13:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,将沿着身为人类的道路前进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起 我说过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我才应该道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对大家 对东乡讲了过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:15:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办 世界 世界要终结了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是友奈的错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如果世界就这样终结
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是无可奈何的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,牛鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,将作为人类战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者不屈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,无论几次都能重振旗鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为了友奈的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,只要去做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,总会有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者就是靠毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,火焰正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,和平常的不一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,牛鬼你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回来…了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,神树大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了 散华…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一如既往的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了友奈 身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,烙印消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
